Package: Shiny
Title: Visualising Trajectories in D. melanogaster
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Philipp",
           family = "Antczak",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "pantczak@uni-koeln.de")
Description: Utilises datasets of days 1, 5, 14, 30, and 37 to derive
    trajectories for genes/proteins of interest. Provides an interactive
    sidebar for gene input, a plotly-based trajectory plot, and a median
    expression summary table.
